{"tid":571753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔清潔工昏迷 送院不治","createTime":"2018-02-25T03:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T03:27:29.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b201ce4547e42ce98f4256180b31ed450185956","tid":571753,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:25:37.000Z","msg":"大埔鄉事會街9-15號寶香樓，早上約7時，65歲清潔男工人被街坊發現昏迷在後巷樓梯，於是報警。救護員到場發現事主沒有呼吸脈搏，將他送那打素醫院搶救，證實不治。警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180225/large/1519527656_18d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180225%2Flarge%2F1519527656_18d0.jpg&h=019b33f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工友事後在場拜祭。(張家豪攝)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180225/57872567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57872567&d=XyEbFIQmaurJHCY37uFycCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1cf1a84f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180225%2F57872567&h=2c72d778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180225/57872567</a>"},{"pid":"7bd6f3152a2d286643e4debb4a25d94e86a74304","tid":571753,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:27:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}